high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.  Turn right and face the counter with the dishwasher in it.
Pick up the fork from the counter above the dishwasher and in front of the canisters.
Turn right, walk to the refrigerator.  Turn left to face the refrigerator.
Open refrigerator door, place the fork in the cup on the second shelf down.
Lift the cup with the spoon in it, close the refrigerator door.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Place the cup with the spoon on the counter to the right, above the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Put a fork in a cup, and move the cup to a counter.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the sink, turn left, go to the counter
Pick up the fork on the counter
Turn right, go forward, turn left in front of the fridge, open the fridge
Put the fork into the glass in the middle shelf of the fridge
Take the glass with the fork in it, close the fridge
Turn left, go towards the sink
Put the glass on the counter to the right
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a fork in it on the counter

high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the sink
Pick up a fork from the counter
Move to the fridge to the right of you
Put the fork inside a cup
Pick up the cup with the fork inside and close the door
Move to the counter to the right of the sink
Place the cup on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cup with a fork on the counter.
